casebody.data:
BALDWIN-NAZARENE
v.
WESTIN HOTEL CINCINNATI 2018-1357 Supreme Court of Ohio. December 19, 2018

O'CONNOR, C.J., and O'DONNELL, FRENCH, FISCHER, DEWINE, and DEGENARO, JJ., concur.

MERIT DECISION WITHOUT OPINION

On S.Ct.Prac.R. 12.04 determination. Cause dismissed. Relator's motion to file evidence in support denied.

KENNEDY, J., concurs in dismissing the cause but would grant relator's motion to file evidence.
